# Binding

Bindable properties for Python.

# Install

```bash
python3 -m pip install binding
```

# Usage

```python
import binding

...
```

# Dependencies

To archive this nice API we have to utilize `curse` from the [forbiddenfruit](https://pypi.org/project/forbiddenfruit/) package.

